      "representation": "view",
      "value": "<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"900\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544636929/Blender_R26_Header.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432683850&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=900&amp;height=492\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544636929/Blender_R26_Header.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432683850&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"700\" data-width=\"1280\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544636943\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"Blender_R26_Header.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544636929\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"d13f6cba-5b8b-4202-b2a1-e19bfcc28453\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544636929/Blender_R26_Header.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432683850&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1800&amp;height=984 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544636929/Blender_R26_Header.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432683850&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=900&amp;height=492 1x\"></span><p><span class=\"legacy-color-text-default\">RenderMan for Blender (RfB) provides easy access to RenderMan features via Blender.</span><br/><br/><span class=\"legacy-color-text-default\">The addon also connects Blender with RenderMan Pro Server in new ways, leading to fast interactive results without the need of writing RIB. The RIB-out functionality continues to support existing pipelines and farm rendering. </span><br/><br/><span class=\"legacy-color-text-default\">RfB provides truly seamless access to RenderMan's speed, power, and stability for Blender users, who can maintain a simple, Blender-centric workflow, or take advantage of the plugins' flexibility to create an optimal, customized pipeline.</span></p><p /><div class=\"confluence-information-macro confluence-information-macro-information conf-macro output-block\" data-hasbody=\"true\" data-macro-id=\"fa987d06-2f41-4e0f-9586-bc3fe998b6d6\" data-macro-name=\"info\"><span class=\"aui-icon aui-icon-small aui-iconfont-info confluence-information-macro-icon\"> </span><div class=\"confluence-information-macro-body\"><h3 id=\"RenderMan27forBlender-Installation\">Installation</h3><p>RenderMan for Blender requires the installation of RenderMan Pro Server as well as the RfB plugin in order to function correctly. See the <a href=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/RFB27/pages/544636971/Installation+of+RenderMan+for+Blender\" rel=\"nofollow\">Installation instructions</a> for more information.</p></div></div>"
